title: CNN.Presents.Gods.Warriors.3of3.Christian.Warriors
description: CNN Presents: God&#039;s Warriors is a three-part series, which is an interesting report on passionate followers of three monotheistic religions: Judaism, Islam, and Christianity. A casual check of the blogosphere finds devotees from each faith fuming about Christiane Amanpour&#039;s investigation. She examines some of the motivations behind "God&#039;s Warriors," and the resulting conflict between each religion and secular society.
